snippet.title: Myth of Empires Announcement Trailer | Coming February 2024
snippet.description:
Myth of Empires Version 1.0 arrives February 2024. Survive, build fortresses, command armies in massive battles, siege enemy cities, and establish your own empire!

Wishlist now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1371580/
Join our Discord: discord.gg/mythofempires
